{"tid":533671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【租香港油輪】涉偷運油給北韓 高雄商人吞藥輕生","createTime":"2018-01-19T04:38:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T04:58:20.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"57fbcf86c500be77e642e4061abfd391ddd2baa7","tid":533671,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T04:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180119/large/1516335462_afd2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180119%2Flarge%2F1516335462_afd2.jpg&h=d6a4c600&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n承租的香港註冊油輪「方向永嘉號」（Lighthouse Winmore），在公海駁油供應北韓的高雄漁業公司負責人陳世憲，在高雄檢調介入偵辦後獲准保釋。不過今早10時許傳出陳世憲在鹽埕區住所吞安眠藥自殺，當局接報後將垈送院，搶救後目前仍有生命危險。<br />\n<br />\n「方向永嘉號」在公海將油轉給北韓，被發現後油輪遭到扣查，調查發現是由台灣公司承租。台灣當局接報後，比對資料，發現油輪是由53歲的高洋漁業公司負責人陳世憲承租，出口報關事項疑有不實申報，傳召陳世憲與船務代理公司相關人員問話。<br />\n<br />\n當時陳表示他長期從事油品買賣生意，這次是透過一名大陸男子介紹，由他承租油輪裝載油品，赴公海交貨，但委託人並未告知他油品實際上是要運往北韓。<br />\n<br />\n檢方問話後，對陳的供詞持有保留態度，但他申報出口報單時，將目的地寫成香港，檢察官認為他涉嫌觸犯偽造文書罪，要求他以150萬元新台幣（約39.8萬港元）保釋，限制出境。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180119/57726771\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180119%2F57726771&d=gOWvjm7v2wDT3Waua6LgiHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=ad6e66f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180119%2F57726771&h=4966e110\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180119/57726771</a>"},{"pid":"6531983785807d91ce1acfb0b08c8efc8516e005","tid":533671,"uid":42921,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T04:42:07.000Z","msg":"被自殺"},{"pid":"6b68216364d0a863f5ecf130683d4f18c59bf067","tid":533671,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T04:47:29.000Z","msg":"高雄人 民主黨鐵票倉不意外<br />\n激化南北韓對台灣好帶利<br />\n當年就係韓戰幫左台灣擋住中共"},{"pid":"d8866a3f6278b955786954aaf4e633c1a1f16f9e","tid":533671,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6b68216364d0a863f5ecf130683d4f18c59bf067","tid":533671,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T04:47:29.000Z","msg":"高雄人 民主黨鐵票倉不意外<br />\n激化南北韓對台灣好帶利<br />\n當年就係韓戰幫左台灣擋住中共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T04:47:41.000Z","msg":"民進黨"},{"pid":"cccf208243dec58934a6065d8983aec906843b62","tid":533671,"uid":126731,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6b68216364d0a863f5ecf130683d4f18c59bf067","tid":533671,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T04:47:29.000Z","msg":"高雄人 民主黨鐵票倉不意外<br />\n激化南北韓對台灣好帶利<br />\n當年就係韓戰幫左台灣擋住中共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T04:49:52.000Z","msg":"垃圾五毛狗玩抹黑都打錯字. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nShow Blocked User - 哥是個傳說"},{"pid":"9c089e3ca68ce433a53f975e0ec93559387d1571","tid":533671,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T04:51:20.000Z","msg":"滅口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d0300ac88c136c69a18181f729695d45909160","tid":533671,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T04:58:20.000Z","msg":"被吞安眠藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}